title: DS330.07 Vertex Indexes | DataStax Enterprise 6 Graph
description:
#DataStaxAcademy #DS330
DS330.07 Vertex Indexes
In order to optimize traversals over your data, DataStax Enterprise Graph makes a few types of indexes available. In this unit, we will go over vertex indexes in detail.
